text: Þys <synden> wa lande gemer atte Kyngesbury.
Erest on Pedridan op alang stremes on Lambrokes gemoure.
Op alang Lambrokes to Schepton gemer to we þrires dyke.
Adoun þer to þere lake lancke þere dyke adoun to Foulenbroke.
Alang Foulenbroke out on a Moure to þan Northlangpulle.
Forþ by Lanpulle by Northen Pendanmede wyþ Myddelnyes Lanpulle.
Of þan Lanpulle to þornylake fornegen Thorny Myddewarde on Southhal.
Oþ on an lake fornegen Esthele yn an Horsyes Northlandpulle.
Forþ out on an Moure est on Pedrenstreme.
